title: Chiefs qualify for IEM Oakland!
body: Did you guys hear what Spawn said on the caster desk today? - good news :)

replies.body:
http://www.memegasms.com/media/created/vhyfxm.jpg

I am excited to see chiefs play at IEM Oakland =D

TSM Immortals Splyce Flash wolves and EDG,i like the chiefs as much as the next OCE player but come on this competition

[edit] just looked into who they had to beat to qualify, if chiefs truly are better than those teams than maybe they could beat splycee and flash wolves

Never said we were going to beat them, just being able to play against these bigger teams for a region like OCE is a brilliant thing for us and I'm personally excited for them win or lose, they're going to learn a lot from this trip.
Doesn't change anything, TSM and Splyce will be replaced by lower ranking teams in both the EU and NA LCS, which will still be great for the oceanic scene.
